column10: Its so cute and I love it! I'll always play this while my mom watching and said to my mom that I will make her breakfast, but I don't really like that u force people to share a feedback.. I hope you will fix it sooner!

Absolutely trash. Got an ad before I even got to play, and the game itself sucks. There's no real interaction at all because everything is done for you. Yet the worst part of all of this is that I was FORCED to rate the game before I could continue past the first level! This was an entire 15 minutes of my life wasted on the absolute dumpster fire you had the audacity to call a game. So here's your disgustingly forced rating. 1 star your game is trash delete it and go fix yourself!
